44:34.370 --> 44:35.370
started just relaxing, and suddenly they found
it was Shri Krishna.  He said, “This valundar,”

44:35.370 --> 44:36.370
means this, this cunning fellow, “is running
after me, now do you think I may escape him?

44:36.370 --> 44:37.370
