are built in Bhairavi and then you will see

45:40.370 --> 45:41.370
how he keeps to that. He keeps to that

45:41.370 --> 45:42.370
Wow, wow! It’s the Heart Chakra. It’s
the Heart Chakra of Shiva.

45:42.370 --> 45:43.370
